			<h6>JOIN THE BED &amp; BREAD CLUB TODAY</h6>

			<p>
				We are fully committed to meeting the direct needs of struggling families and individuals here in our community. But we can't help them without your support. By becoming a member of the Bed &amp; Bread Club, your monthly gift will make a real difference in the lives of the people we serve every day.
			</p>

